Package is.merkor.core.redis.dictionaries

Contains implementations of dictionaries and parsers to access MerkOr data from a Redis server

See:
          Description

Class Summary
MerkorRedisConstants All constants used in the Redis representation of the MerkOr data.
RedisClusterDictionary An implementation of the ClusterDictionary interface using a Redis representation of the MerkOr data.
RedisClusterMemberDictionary An implementation of the ClusterMemberDictionary interface to access ClusterMembers stored in Redis format.
RedisClusterMemberParser Parses data from Redis and provides methods to retrieve Clusters and ClusterMembers.
RedisClusterParser Parses data from Redis and provides methods to retrieve Clusters.
RedisConnectionCheck  
RedisItemDictionary An implementation of the ItemDictionary interface using RedisItemParser to connect to a Redis server containing MerkOr data.
RedisItemParser  
RedisRelationDictionary An implementation of the RelationDictionary interface using RedisRelationParser to connect to a Redis server containing MerkOr data.
RedisRelationParser Provides methods to parse keys and values from MerkOr data on a Redis server, and instantiates RedisItems from the parsed information.
